FBIS4-46423 "jptot024__l94100" JPRS-TOT-94-024-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 7 June 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA Explosion Near Moscow Train Station Leaves Dead, Injured Explosion Near Moscow Train Station Leaves Dead, Injured LD0706155794 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1511 GMT 7 Jun 94 LD0706155794 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Larisa Kislinskaya] [Text] Moscow, 7 Jun (ITAR-TASS) -- The TASS correspondent was told at Moscow's main interior affairs directorate that an unidentified explosive device went off at the "Vityaz" restaurant, near Paveletskiy train station. The explosion occurred at 1730. According to preliminary data there are dead and wounded. [See "Selected Video Reports" section for TV coverage.]
